title: Eddie’s Wine Taste Challenge + Miranda Lambert Talks About New Music And Her Wedding Anniversary + 90’s One Hit Wonder Game!

description:
Eddie claims to have a sophisticated pallet when it comes to wine. So today he tasted 4 bottles of wine. 3 of them will cheap bottles of wine and 1 Expensive. He is trying to determine which bottle is the expensive one. We talk to Miranda Lambert about hew new album announcement and traveling around the country with her husband. Bobby plays a famous one hit wonder song…the show has to name the 90’s artist.
